    "title": "Bleed: permanent production halt",
    "body": "Lab L2 unlocks Bleed (35 units).\n\nBleed targets a node and drains 1 unit/sec from it permanently — until that node is captured by someone other than its current owner. Production halts while bleeding.\n\nThe enemy's main base produces too fast to take by force. Bleed it. Push in."
